Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.cli

Class CLI

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.cli.CLI
All Implemented Interfaces:
UI, java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.lang.Runnable, java.util.EventListener
public class CLI
extends java.lang.Object
implements UI, java.lang.Runnable
Main CLI client class manages the game if the player decides to play with Command Line Interface.
